# Per-Dockerfile ignore file for Dockerfile.test (BuildKit picks this up
# automatically when the file is named `<Dockerfile>.dockerignore`).
#
# Unlike the root `.dockerignore` (which strips `tests/`, `docs/`, `*.md`
# to keep the production runtime image lean), the test runner image NEEDS
# the test sources. Override the relevant exclusions here.

# Always exclude
.git
.github
target
.claude
.vscode
.DS_Store
*.swp
*.swo
*~
perftest

# Test runner explicitly NEEDS these (do NOT exclude):
# - tests/    (where the actual test sources live)
# - docs/     (some tests reference docs/ paths)
# - *.md      (CLAUDE.md is checked by some tests)
